WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.543
- Hen... Hen...
- No.

00:00:02.627 --> 00:00:05.587
- Having a good night?
- Yes,

00:00:05.672 --> 00:00:08.340
It's... it's right up there
with my father's funeral

00:00:08.424 --> 00:00:10.300
for sheer entertainment value.

00:00:11.386 --> 00:00:15.222
- I thought you'd gone.
- No. Hamish took the Edinburgh sleeper.

00:00:15.306 --> 00:00:17.391
I'm off now.
Keep me company?

